Money (for PHP)
====

A library for dealing with money and currency conversion.
PHP port of http://money.rubyforge.org

Usage
----

    <?php

    require_once 'src/money.php';

    // 10.00 USD
    $money = new money\Money(1000, 'USD');
    $money->cents();     // => 1000
    $money->currency();  // => new money\Currency("USD")


